name: bundlesize

scripts.test: npm run test:default && npm run test:no-compression && npm run test:brotli-compression
scripts.test:brotli-compression: cat pipe.js | node pipe --compression brotli --name pipe.js
scripts.test:default: node index && cat pipe.js | node pipe --name pipe.js --max-size 1kB
scripts.test:no-compression: cat pipe.js | node pipe --compression none --name pipe.js
